NpU" rel style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); text-decoration: underline;">Grea=
t Filter</a><span> for Vertically Integrated companies: &#8220;Almost all o=
f the largest companies are vertically integrated. Almost none of the small=
 ones are.&#8221;&#160;</span></p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-=
size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Robin Hanson dreamed up=
 the Great Filter to address a mystery: where are the aliens?&#160;</p><blo=
ckquote style=3D"border-left: 4px solid #0c2427; margin: 20px 0; padding: 0=
;"><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; =
margin: 0 0 20px 0; margin-left: 20px;"><em><span>Humanity seems to have a =
bright future, i.e., a non-trivial chance of expanding to fill the universe=
 with lasting life. But the fact that space near us seems dead now tells us=
 that any given piece of dead matter faces an astronomically low chance of =
begating such a future. </span><strong>There thus exists a great filter bet=
ween death and expanding lasting life.</strong></em></p></blockquote><p sty=
le=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0=
 0 20px 0;"><span>In his telling, as we discussed in the </span><a href=3D"=
https://substack.com/redirect/92537c65-8ed7-42ef-b84d-1210bb324c21?j=3DeyJ1=
IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU" rel style=3D"co=
lor: rgb(54, 55, 55); text-decoration: underline;">Deep Dive on Fuse</a><sp=
an>, something must get in the way between where we are now, on the cusp of=
 universal expansion, and actually realizing that potential to expand. Mayb=
e it&#8217;s climate change. Maybe it&#8217;s nuclear war. Maybe it&#8217;s=
 global pandemic.&#160;&#160;</span></p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55);=
 font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">There are a numbe=
r of reasons a civilization might not make the leap from computers, rockets=
, and nuclear power to intergalactic travel. Better understanding them may =
help us pass through the Great Filter and out into the universe.&#160;</p><=
p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; marg=
in: 0 0 20px 0;">Similarly, there are many reasons a Vertical Integrator ma=
y not make it from small, complex, wildly ambitious startup to large, domin=
ant company. Understanding them may help companies pass through that Great =
Filter of their own.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size=
: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">So in the third of our four=
-part series on Vertical Integrators, we&#8217;ll dig into what makes them =
so challenging.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16p=
x; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">While the specific difficulties =
faced by modern Vertical Integrators are more numerous than the companies t=
hemselves, there are seven categories that I want to focus on:&#160;</p><ol=
 style=3D"margin-top: 0; padding: 0;"><li style=3D"margin: 8px 0 0 32px;"><=
p style=3D"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px;=
 line-height: 26px; margin: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-left: 4px;">It req=
uires building at least two companies: software and hardware.&#160;</p></li=
><li style=3D"margin: 8px 0 0 32px;"><p style=3D"box-sizing: border-box; co=
lor: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0; margin=
-bottom: 0; padding-left: 4px;">Hardware by itself is just really hard.&#16=
0;</p></li><li style=3D"margin: 8px 0 0 32px;"><p style=3D"box-sizing: bord=
er-box; color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin:=
 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-left: 4px;">Incumbents are good at what they =
do and have advantages.&#160;</p></li><li style=3D"margin: 8px 0 0 32px;"><=
p style=3D"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px;=
 line-height: 26px; margin: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-left: 4px;">Figuri=
ng out the right level of integration is not obvious.&#160;</p></li><li sty=
le=3D"margin: 8px 0 0 32px;"><p style=3D"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb=
(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0; margin-bottom:=
 0; padding-left: 4px;">You can&#8217;t pivot nearly as easily.&#160;</p></=
li><li style=3D"margin: 8px 0 0 32px;"><p style=3D"box-sizing: border-box; =
color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0; marg=
in-bottom: 0; padding-left: 4px;">Something better might come along.&#160;<=
/p></li><li style=3D"margin: 8px 0 0 32px;"><p style=3D"box-sizing: border-=
box; color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0;=
 margin-bottom: 0; padding-left: 4px;">Getting to revenue takes a lot of mo=
ney.&#160;</p></li></ol><h3 class=3D"header-anchor-post" style=3D"--highlig=
ht-bg: rgba(var(--color-bg-accent-themed-rgb), 0.2); -moz-appearance: optim=
