;"><strong>Something Better Might Come Along</strong></h3><p style=3D"color=
: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"=
>This might be the most pernicious of the challenges.&#160;&#160;</p><p sty=
le=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0=
 0 20px 0;"><span>Imagine doing all of the hard things required to get a Ve=
rtical Integrator to enough scale to get product quality and costs to a com=
