n></p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26p=
x; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">With the pace of technological advancement happenin=
g right now, that&#8217;s always a very real possibility.&#160;</p><p style=
=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0=
 20px 0;">One of my favorite questions to ask founders is, &#8220;What sci-=
fi technology are you most worried about obsoleting your approach?&#8221;&#=
160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 2=
6px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>It&#8217;s an absurd question on its face, =
but </span><a href=3D"https://substack.com/redirect/eb5707bf-a43c-4c93-993d=
