kRNpU" rel style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); text-decoration: underline;">sc=
i-fi has a way of coming true</a><span>, and the absurdity helps me get to =
the question I&#8217;m going for, which is: how close to the best possible =
approach is what you&#8217;re planning to build.&#160;</span></p><p style=
=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0=
 20px 0;">As a non-Vertical Integrator example, think about building an AI =
