r GPT-4 as GPT-4 was over GPT-3, we&#8217;re in trouble,&#8221; then you&#8=
217;re probably in trouble. If it&#8217;s &#8220;AGI might be an issue if i=
t&#8217;s able to do everything in the world,&#8221; you might be safer.&#1=
60;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26=
px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>In energy, if the answer is &#8220;</span><a=
 href=3D"https://substack.com/redirect/3348a13f-501b-4caa-896b-ae13b3a140b6=
?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU" rel st=
